{
  "stem": "7093.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I couldn't get up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And these men said that they are going to the American liberation center, which is 29 kilometers from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, well, I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no way I could get onto my feet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so I said, I'm sorry, I would love to come with them, but I can't.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then, as they were leaving, one of them said he's not leaving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He's going to look after me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he really looked after me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he became the first man in my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was-- I was very much in love because he was a human being who-- five years he was as prisoner of war-- or four-- and now, instead of rushing home, is looking after me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he is seeing that I get onto to my feet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, well, it seemed that we were both very much in love.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because I was telling him what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my spirit was somehow still, still there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And anyway, I-- he said, would I marry him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Now I said already before that French-- everything that's French, for me, was fantastic-- French films, French-- even this-- And there was another thing, that in camp I found that actually the simple people, the uneducated people, they were more decent than the sophisticated-- more sophisticated people.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this was a completely unsophisticated, uneducated man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he was French and spoke beautiful French.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I-- and he was decent to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I really fell in love.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am going to go to France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I am going to get married.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything-- life is going to be wonderful from now on.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
